			h2 Comparison between corpora
			
			p  Figure 3 shows the word frequency vs count plot for the different corpora, for only the words present in the Dictionary. One can see how the Wikipedia and the HJK corpora are similar.
			
			p  In Figure 4 are the most frequent words present in each corpus. It's interesting to see how different words rank differently in frequency for each corpus, with the Open Subtitles corpus showing the greater discrepancies.
			
